    Models\r\nDavid Guillen Jr\r\nAden Lopez\r\nSamuel Saeger\r\nKennedy Taylor\r\n\r\nCreature
    Animations\r\nDavid Guillen Jr\r\nAden Lopez\r\nSamuel Saeger\r\nKennedy Taylor\r\n\r\nPlayer/Keeper
    Models\r\nKennedy Taylor\r\n\r\nOther Animal Models\r\nRachel Ridge\r\n\r\nOther
    Animal Animations\r\nRachel Ridge\r\n\r\nRigging\r\nRachel Ridge\r\nSamuel Saeger\r\nKennedy
