    Guillen Jr\r\nRachel Ridge\r\n\r\nUI Designers\r\nMarshall Turner\r\nRachel Ridge\r\n\r\nIntro
    Animation\r\nRachel Ridge\r\n\r\nProgramming\r\nLead\r\nWeston Tollette\r\n\r\nFishing\r\nWeston
    Tollette\r\n\r\nCreature UI\r\nWeston Tollette\r\n\r\nDialogue System\r\nMarshall
    Turner\r\n\r\nEverything Else\r\nWeston Tollette\r\n\r\nSpecial Effects\r\nParticles\r\nAden
    Lopez\r\nSamuel Saeger\r\nMarshall Turner (Rain)\r\n\r\nLevel Design\r\nLead\r\nMarshall
    Turner\r\n\r\nIsland Scenes\r\nMarshall Turner\r\n\r\nFishing Scenes\r\nMarshall
    Turner\r\n\r\nDeath Scenes\r\nAden Lopez\r\nKennedy Taylor\r\nWeston Tollette\r\n\r\nHouse
